      <title>反对派首长领导候选人关注韩国总统职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/opposition-chief-leads-candidates-eyeing-south-korean-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在宪法法院坚持Yoon Suk Yeol的弹each之后，韩国下一任总统的竞赛开始了，永久将他撤职。少数候选人将争夺该国在选举之前的最高职位，必须在6月3日之前举行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/opposition-chief-leads-candidates-eyeing-south-korean-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 06:11:24 GMT</pubDate>
